        <body>
        <div type="letter">
        <opener><dateline><date when=""><!--Write the date here --><dateline></date><salute>Dear <persName key="harriet_monroe">Harriet</persName>:</salute>
        </opener>
           <p>Leave my name where it is if you like to do so. I think it is better not in the list of guarantors, and I thank you for taking it out, but otherwise it is all right. I shall look forward to your short poem in March and your long series in April with great pleasure.</p>
            <p>I read <title key="appuldercombePark" level="a">"Appuldercombe Park"</title> at a reading <above>on</above> Wednesday, and it was well received.</p>
            <closure>Affectionately yours,</closure>
        </div>
